(46, 1, 13, 44, 2, 38, 38, 'baptized in the name of Paul', 'Baptism in Christ''s Name', 'This connection highlights the importance of baptism in the name of Jesus Christ as a unifying act among believers. Both passages emphasize the significance of being baptized, with 1 Corinthians questioning divisions and Acts affirming baptism for remission of sins.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(46, 1, 13, 44, 10, 48, 48, 'baptized in the name of Paul', 'Baptism in Christ''s Name', 'Both passages emphasize the act of baptism and its association with the name of Christ. In 1 Corinthians, Paul questions whether believers were baptized in his name, while Acts highlights baptism in the name of the Lord, underscoring the importance of Christ''s authority in the sacrament.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(46, 1, 13, 46, 10, 2, 2, 'baptized in the name of Paul', 'Baptism and Unity in Christ', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of baptism as a unifying act. In 1 Corinthians 1:13, Paul questions divisions among believers, while 1 Corinthians 10:2 highlights the collective baptism of the Israelites under Moses, suggesting a theme of unity through baptism.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(46, 1, 13, 47, 5, 14, 15, 'Christ divided? was Paul crucified for you?', 'Unity in Christ''s Sacrifice', 'Both passages emphasize the significance of Christ''s death and its implications for believers. In 1 Corinthians, the question of division among followers highlights the centrality of Christ, while 2 Corinthians speaks to living for Him who died for all.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(46, 1, 13, 40, 28, 19, 19, 'baptized in the name of Paul', 'Baptism in Christ''s Name', 'Both passages emphasize the act of baptism, with 1 Corinthians questioning the division among followers and Matthew instructing to baptize in the name of the Father, Son, and Holy Ghost. This connection highlights the importance of unity in the practice of baptism.', 'theme', 0.321, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
