(46, 8, 9, 48, 5, 13, 13, 'liberty of yours', 'Connection of Christian Liberty', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of liberty in the Christian life. 1 Corinthians warns against using liberty as a stumbling block, while Galatians encourages using liberty to serve others in love.', 'theme', 0.426, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
