(46, 8, 10, 46, 8, 4, 4, NULL, 'Connection of Knowledge and Idols', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of eating things offered to idols. The first verse discusses the impact of knowledge on the conscience of the weak, while the second asserts that an idol is nothing, highlighting the tension between knowledge and belief.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
