(46, 9, 1, 44, 9, 17, 17, 'have I not seen Jesus Christ our Lord?', 'Connection of Apostleship and Vision', 'This connection highlights Paul''s claim of apostleship through his encounter with Jesus, as noted in both passages. In Acts, Ananias acknowledges the appearance of Jesus to Saul, affirming his role as an apostle.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
