(46, 9, 2, 47, 12, 12, 12, 'seal of mine apostleship are ye', 'Apostolic Authority and Signs', 'This connection highlights the affirmation of Paul''s apostleship through the evidence of signs and wonders. Both passages emphasize the validation of Paul''s role as an apostle among the Corinthians.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
