(46, 9, 3, 46, 14, 37, 37, 'Mine answer to them that do examine me is this,', 'Authority in Apostolic Teaching', 'This connection highlights the theme of authority in Paul''s writings. Both passages emphasize the need for acknowledgment of his teachings as authoritative, with 1 Corinthians 9:3 addressing examination and 1 Corinthians 14:37 asserting his words as commandments.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
