(46, 9, 3, 47, 12, 16, 19, 'Mine answer to them that do examine me is this', 'Defense of Apostolic Authority', 'Both passages emphasize the defense of Paul''s actions and integrity in ministry. In 1 Corinthians, he addresses those examining him, while in 2 Corinthians, he reiterates his commitment to not burden the church, highlighting his sincerity and the shared mission with his companions.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
